            2. How We Use Your Information
        </h2>

        <p data-end="1273" data-start="1253">We use your data to:</p>

        <ul data-end="1511" data-start="1274">
            <li data-end="1312" data-start="1274">
                <p data-end="1312" data-start="1276">
                    Provide and personalize our services
                </p>
            </li>
            <li data-end="1365" data-start="1313">
                <p data-end="1365" data-start="1315">
