                </p>
            </li>
            <li data-end="1786" data-start="1732">
                <p data-end="1786" data-start="1734">
                    With your permission (e.g. integrating with Spotify)
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>

        <hr data-end="1791" data-start="1788" />
        <h2 data-end="1823" data-start="1793">4. Cookies and Tracking</h2>

        <p data-end="1842" data-start="1824">We use cookies to:</p>

        <ul data-end="1925" data-start="1843">
            <li data-end="1863" data-start="1843">
                <p data-end="1863" data-start="1845">Keep you logged in</p>
            </li>
            <li data-end="1891" data-start="1864">
                <p data-end="1891" data-start="1866">
                    Remember your preferences
                </p>
            </li>
            <li data-end="1925" data-start="1892">
                <p data-end="1925" data-start="1894">
                    Track basic usage for analytics
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>

        <p data-end="2009" data-start="1927">
            You can disable cookies in your browser, but some features may not
            work correctly.
        </p>

        <hr data-end="2014" data-start="2011" />
        <h2 data-end="2051" data-start="2016">5. Data Storage and Security</h2>

        <p data-end="2184" data-start="2052">
            Your data is stored on secure servers. We use standard industry
            practices to protect your information, but no system is 100% secure.
        </p>

        <hr data-end="2189" data-start="2186" />
