        </p>

        <hr data-end="2840" data-start="2837" />
        <h2 data-end="2874" data-start="2842">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>

        <p data-end="3004" data-start="2875">
            We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. Changes will be
            posted on this page, with an updated &quot;Effective Date&quot; at
            the top.
        </p>

        <hr data-end="3009" data-start="3006" />
        <h2 data-end="3032" data-start="3011">10. Contact Us</h2>

        <p data-end="3138" data-start="3033">
            If you have any questions or concerns about your privacy, please
